{"tid":2302101,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"疫症橫行 加速「日本製造」大流行 Unicharm（ユニ・チャーム）口罩大熱賣","createTime":"2020-11-27T00:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T01:55:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0874800fcf8d0c46f224856d5355c2a9b7c60a","tid":2302101,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"年初，本港疫情最嚴重，而口罩最匱乏之時，藥房售賣的日製口罩甚至索價上千，其中一個炒價最高的口罩品牌是 「Unicharm」（ユニ・チャーム）。此「口罩名牌」本以生產女性衛生用品、紙尿片起家，自 1995 年就開始生產口罩。在武漢肺炎來襲日本後，該公司位於觀音寺市工廠開始 24 小時營運，安排更多工人生產口罩，現時每月可產出達 1.2 億個口罩，是過去的 3 倍。即使疫情蔓延期間，陸續有他國企業加入口罩生產，「日本製造」仍然是 Unicharm 的致勝之道。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯Unicharm 行政總裁高原豪久接受「日經亞洲」訪問時指，「將利用在日本的（口罩製作）經驗」來擴大亞洲市場。目前企業生產的口罩會先應付疫情下的需求，但長遠來說， 其口罩在亞洲地區亦有市場，例如雅加達、新加坡、曼谷、新德里等地居民，仍要應對嚴重的空氣污染。高原相信，無論流行病何時退卻，對高品質口罩的需求依然會保持強勁。<br />\n<br />\n在相關市場中，Unicharm 目前其中一個最大的競爭對手之一，是中國的比亞迪。後者業務以智能電話電池、電動汽車、太陽能電池板為主，自今年初開始更成為全球最大口罩製造商之一，其每天能生產 1.16 億個口罩，並將產品運送到 50 個國家。但即使中國企業有驚人的生產能力，高原仍相信日製口罩對亞洲消費者具吸引力，他直指：「需求比我預期的還要強勁。日本 Unicharm 口罩在亞洲供不應求。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/11/27/made-in-japan-is-still-competitive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2Fmade-in-japan-is-still-competitive%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=a01fd4df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/11/27/made-in-japan-is-still-competitive/</a>"},{"pid":"3f33a548a7c474f9020024db14eaff00bbc2702c","tid":2302101,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"兩舊水/30個🙄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d89ge5hfdpmo8.cloudfront.net/mall/4903111961016n_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd89ge5hfdpmo8.cloudfront.net%2Fmall%2F4903111961016n_l.jpg&h=72a16c0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5683c35b7b4c655f8bee3f7960075882fe81674","tid":2302101,"uid":20713,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:02:24.000Z","msg":"超快適好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6d120f9025da67a42dfba09fd14c61c4f48714","tid":2302101,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"好歌"},{"pid":"24adb55e3a53462e328f8162cd1ddd7827dc9800","tid":2302101,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255c1cee5e29661a21f250d6d3238d86370803de","tid":2302101,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲應該可以unlock faceid"},{"pid":"181353b3b46468c47eda583973963d584258e2a3","tid":2302101,"uid":92002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"超快適條粗帶 = 身份象徵 社會賢達"},{"pid":"ed4ba874b030108a02702bb109924888b79c569b","tid":2302101,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"超立體有陣紙質嘅香味"},{"pid":"79797c06c06422ebf11e8f6682bacb702bd0d0f3","tid":2302101,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"唔反對用日本製造unicharm<br />\n<br />\n不過我用開台灣製造外科口罩，$150 一盒，50個"},{"pid":"6868e9ee73f6672fb5664f6a58ed75a80a7989a9","tid":2302101,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:37:59.000Z","msg":"超立体係唔錯 只係無鼻線講野好易離罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77e2d9f98f7688a6078f410124bf9099a23245a","tid":2302101,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"超立體冇鐵線易漏氣<br />\n超快適夏天戴隨時窒息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef887b3731c94dc03aca64d3750b9b68d4ddb9f","tid":2302101,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f33a548a7c47